        public ManagedFunctionFlowTypeBuilder<F> setLabel​(java.lang.String label)
        Description copied from interface: ManagedFunctionFlowTypeBuilder

        Provides means to specify a display label for the Flow.

        This need not be set as is only an aid to better identify the Flow. If not set the ManagedFunctionTypeBuilder will use the following order to get a display label:

        1. Enum key name
        2. index value
